---
title: Seared Chicken, Creamy Leek Sauce & Mash Kids' Dinner: Chicken & Leek Potato Topped Pie
description: Enjoy one meal, two ways with our + Kids Dinner range. Cook a delicious dinner for the adults, and at the same time create a kid-friendly meal for the kids with a simple twist. Turn a juicy chicken drizzled in a creamy leek sauce on top of a fluffy mash into a veggie chicken pie, topped with potato.

